      <title>圣詹姆斯广场因 4.26 亿英镑费用和股息削减而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/st-james-s-place-plunges-most-since-2016-after-dividend-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的财富管理公司为潜在客户退款拨备了 4.26 亿英镑（合 5.38 亿美元）并削减了投资者支出，导致 St. James&#39;s Place Plc 的股价在伦敦遭遇七年多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/st-james-s-place-plunges-most-since-2016-after-dividend-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
